  "texts": [
    "Large language models (LLMs) are increasingly used in educational applications, acting as AI tutors that engage students in natural language.",
    "However, effective tutoring goes beyond producing correct answers.",
    "AI tutors must recognize student mistakes, explain misconceptions, provide constructive guidance, and suggest actionable next steps.",
    "Assessing such teaching behavior remains challenging.",
    "Prior work in intelligent tutoring systems (ITS) emphasized these goals long before the advent of LLMs."
  ],
